Revision history for Perl module Image::Imlib2::Thumbnail:

0.40 Mon Aug 24 22:12:07 BST 2009
  - have different quality ratio per size (defaults to 75), patch
    by Jos Boumans
  - preserve the image extension (so resized PNGs are PNGs) and 
    report the MIME type, patch by Jos Boumans
  - add human-readable license
  - add abstract to Makefile.PL

0.34 Wed Apr 16 14:41:07 BST 2008
  - be sure to report the right size when not cropping

0.33 Tue Apr 15 14:42:36 BST 2008
  - having a width or height as zero means just scaling, no cropping

0.32 Mon Dec 10 09:09:35 GMT 2007
  - also return the original image
  - add Path::Class to dependencies, remove Perl6::Say

0.31 Fri Dec  7 17:49:35 GMT 2007
  - initial release
